{"id":10660,"date":"2023-02-16T14:43:15","date_gmt":"2023-02-16T09:13:15","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/?p=10660"},"modified":"2023-02-16T14:59:38","modified_gmt":"2023-02-16T09:29:38","slug":"avs-group-and-nocart-join-hands-for-a-sustainable-india","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/2023\/02\/16\/avs-group-and-nocart-join-hands-for-a-sustainable-india\/","title":{"rendered":"AVS GROUP AND NOCART JOIN HANDS FOR A SUSTAINABLE INDIA"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-10679 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/WhatsApp-Image-2023-02-16-at-2.57.12-PM-300x92.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"672\" height=\"206\" srcset=\"https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/WhatsApp-Image-2023-02-16-at-2.57.12-PM-300x92.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/WhatsApp-Image-2023-02-16-at-2.57.12-PM-1024x312.jpeg 1024w, https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/WhatsApp-Image-2023-02-16-at-2.57.12-PM-768x234.jpeg 768w, https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/WhatsApp-Image-2023-02-16-at-2.57.12-PM-1536x468.jpeg 1536w, https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/WhatsApp-Image-2023-02-16-at-2.57.12-PM-600x183.jpeg 600w, https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/WhatsApp-Image-2023-02-16-at-2.57.12-PM.jpeg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 672px) 100vw, 672px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>The <strong>Uttar Pradesh Global Investors Summit 2023<\/strong> was a 3-day investment event organised by the Government of Uttar Pradesh, India. It brought various stakeholders from around the world together, including policymakers, business leaders, and academic experts, to collectively explore business opportunities and forge partnerships worth <strong>$420 Billion* (\u20b933.83 lakh crores)<\/strong>. The event was officially inaugurated by the honorable <strong>Prime Minister of India, Shri Narendra Modi<\/strong>, accompanied by the honorable <strong>Chief Minister of Uttar Pradesh, Shri Yogi Adityanath Singh<\/strong>, and the <strong>Minister of Energy for Uttar Pradesh, Shri A.K. Sharma<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_10666\" style=\"width: 379px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10666\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-10666\" src=\"https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/WhatsApp-Image-2023-02-13-at-3.27.29-PM-300x135.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"369\" height=\"166\" srcset=\"https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/WhatsApp-Image-2023-02-13-at-3.27.29-PM-300x135.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/WhatsApp-Image-2023-02-13-at-3.27.29-PM-1024x461.jpeg 1024w, https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/WhatsApp-Image-2023-02-13-at-3.27.29-PM-768x346.jpeg 768w, https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/WhatsApp-Image-2023-02-13-at-3.27.29-PM-600x270.jpeg 600w, https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/WhatsApp-Image-2023-02-13-at-3.27.29-PM.jpeg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 369px) 100vw, 369px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-10666\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em><strong>L-R:<\/strong> Mr. Abdul Gamel Nasser, Business Financial Associate, AVS Group; Mr. A.K. Sharma, Minister of Energy for Uttar Pradesh; Mr. Vesa Korhonen, Managing Director, Nocart; and Lt. Col. Vijay Tomar (Retd.), Chairman, AVS Group<\/em><\/p><\/div>\n<h2><\/h2>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">About Cleantech Group:<\/h2>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-10663 alignleft\" src=\"https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/CleantechGroup-300x83.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"216\" height=\"60\" srcset=\"https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/CleantechGroup-300x83.jpg 300w, https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/CleantechGroup-768x213.jpg 768w, https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/CleantechGroup-600x167.jpg 600w, https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/CleantechGroup.jpg 900w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 216px) 100vw, 216px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Cleantech Group provides research, consulting, and events to catalyse opportunities for sustainable growth powered by innovation. They have evaluated more than 1,200 companies and represented 19 countries in the 2023 Global Cleantech 100 Companies.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">About Nocart:<\/h2>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-10664 alignleft\" src=\"https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/Nocart-300x96.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"215\" height=\"69\" srcset=\"https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/Nocart-300x96.png 300w, https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/Nocart.png 553w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 215px) 100vw, 215px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Nocart is an environmentally conscious energy company that uses multiple sources to produce high-quality, green electricity for all needs. They are among the top 20 promising companies in Finland, have delivered 50 units of power plants, and have seen a remarkable growth of 323% from last year.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2>AVS Group and Nocart join forces to introduce Renewable Energy solutions in India:<\/h2>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-10667 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/2-1-300x107.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"527\" height=\"188\" srcset=\"https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/2-1-300x107.png 300w, https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/2-1-1024x364.png 1024w, https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/2-1-768x273.png 768w, https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/2-1-1536x546.png 1536w, https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/2-1-2048x728.png 2048w, https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/2-1-600x213.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 527px) 100vw, 527px\" \/><\/h2>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><strong>AVS Group<\/strong> is an India-based Multinational Company with subsidiaries all over Ghana. AVS Group is proud to bring Nocart, a leading member of the Cleantech Consortium, to India. The work will encompass three innovative projects in the fields of Renewable Energy, Compressed Bio Gas, and Bio Pellets. With the signing of <strong>35 Memorandums of Understanding<\/strong> (MoUs) with the Government,<strong> 35 sites<\/strong> has been identified with a portfolio valued at <strong>$2 Billion* (\u20b916,000 crores)<\/strong>, which has the potential to expand to <strong>55 sites<\/strong> worth <strong>$3.5 Billion* (\u20b928,000 crores)<\/strong> of portfolio.<\/p>\n<p>The association shall begin with the inception of three pioneering prime locations &#8211; <strong>Lucknow<\/strong>, with a portfolio of <strong>$1 Billion* (\u20b98,000 crores)<\/strong>, <strong>Basti<\/strong>, with a portfolio of <strong>$37.5 Million* (\u20b9300 crores)<\/strong>, and <strong>Mau<\/strong>, with a portfolio of <strong>$35 Million* (\u20b9280 crores)<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_10669\" style=\"width: 461px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10669\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-10669\" src=\"https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/43b349690545301c43b349690545301c328129-300x117.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"451\" height=\"176\" srcset=\"https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/43b349690545301c43b349690545301c328129-300x117.png 300w, https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/43b349690545301c43b349690545301c328129-1024x398.png 1024w, https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/43b349690545301c43b349690545301c328129-768x299.png 768w, https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/43b349690545301c43b349690545301c328129-1536x597.png 1536w, https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/43b349690545301c43b349690545301c328129-2048x796.png 2048w, https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/43b349690545301c43b349690545301c328129-600x233.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 451px) 100vw, 451px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-10669\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Glimpses of the UP Global Investors Summit 2023<\/em><\/p><\/div>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2>An initiative towards a better India:<\/h2>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-10670 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/Avs-X-Nocart-300x121.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"233\" height=\"94\" srcset=\"https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/Avs-X-Nocart-300x121.png 300w, https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/Avs-X-Nocart-768x311.png 768w, https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/Avs-X-Nocart-600x243.png 600w, https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/Avs-X-Nocart.png 899w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 233px) 100vw, 233px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>AVS Group and Nocart have joined hands for this venture to establish a new enterprise named &#8220;<strong>AVS Nocart Pvt. Ltd.<\/strong>&#8221; The primary objective of this joint venture is to make India a <strong>zero waste country<\/strong> and convert the present waste dump into usable energy by means of <strong>repurposing<\/strong> and <strong>recycling<\/strong>. The transition to clean energy is an enormous economic prospect that has led to a shared commitment to work together to facilitate India&#8217;s growth, industrialisation, and the provision of a better quality of life to its citizens.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-10672 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/9c08a96a44ae40849c08a96a44ae40845-300x121.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"518\" height=\"209\" srcset=\"https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/9c08a96a44ae40849c08a96a44ae40845-300x121.png 300w, https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/9c08a96a44ae40849c08a96a44ae40845-1024x413.png 1024w, https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/9c08a96a44ae40849c08a96a44ae40845-768x310.png 768w, https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/9c08a96a44ae40849c08a96a44ae40845-1536x619.png 1536w, https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/9c08a96a44ae40849c08a96a44ae40845-2048x826.png 2048w, https:\/\/avsgroup.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/9c08a96a44ae40849c08a96a44ae40845-600x242.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 518px) 100vw, 518px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>The latest news has been extensively reported by several renowned <strong>media outlets<\/strong>, such as <a href=\"https:\/\/www.hindustantimes.com\/cities\/lucknow-news\/finnish-firm-to-take-over-waste-management-in-major-up-cities-101676291732617.html\">Hindustan Times<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/solidwasteindia.com\/finland-based-clean-tech-to-manage-waste-in-up\/\">Solid Waste India<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.amarujala.com\/lucknow\/mou-signed-with-new-company-for-waist-management-lucknow-news-lko669567039-2023-02-13\">Amar Ujala<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.constructionworld.in\/urban-infrastructure\/wastewater-and-sewage-treatment\/--clean-tech----to-take-over-waste-management-in-major-up-cities\/39242\">Construction World<\/a>, and many more.<\/p>\n<p>For more updates, follow us on <a href=\"https:\/\/instagram.com\/avsgroupglobal?igshid=YmMyMTA2M2Y=\">Instagram<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/AVSGroup.IND\">Facebook<\/a>, and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.linkedin.com\/company\/avsgroup\/\">LinkedIn<\/a>. If you have any queries or concerns, please feel free to contact us at <strong>info@avsgroup.in<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<p><strong>*<\/strong>The values provided are approximate and should be used as an estimate only.<\/p>\n","